title: Does the picture of Okasio Cortez appear in an immigrant camp?
subtitle: In 2018, Alexandria Okasio Cortez took a photograph before being elected to the United States House, protesting against the immigration detention camp in Texas.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A "newly discovered" photo reveals that Alexandria Okasio Cortez was crying on an empty parking lot, not detained immigrant children, in a demonstration in Texas.
